                     <title>A collection of Asmat prayers</title>
                     <note>Arranged for the days of the week by the original and a later hand, but the manuscript is rebound in disorder</note>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.1"><locus target="#46r" facs="046"/><title>Wednesday</title>
                         <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.1.1">
                            <locus from="42v" to="44r" facs="043"/>
                            <title type="complete" ref="LIT5888AsmatPrayer"> Prayer of mercy that the angels and the clergy prayed</title>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                          ብሰም፡ አብ፡<gap reason="omitted"/>ጸሎተ፡ ምሕረት፡ ዘጸለዩ፡ መላእክት፡ ወሰማዕት፡ ጳጳሳት፡ ወካህናት፡ ወመነኮሳት፡ ዕድ፡ ወአንስት፡ ወኵሎሙ፡ ተጋቢኦሙ፡ ጸለዩ፡ ዘንተ፡ ኀበ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ መሐረኒ፡ መዋዒ፡ ፀር፡
                        </incipit>
                         </msItem>
                         <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.1.2">
                            <locus from="44r" to="44v" facs="044"/>
                            <title type="complete" ref="LIT5888AsmatPrayer"> Prayer to keep Satan away</title>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                          በስመ፡ አብ፡<gap reason="omitted"/>ዘኢይቀርብከ፡ ሰይጣን፡ ዘንተ፡ ድግም፡ ወብል፡ በአስባኤል፡ በአቅናኤል፡ በአማኑኤል፡<gap reason="omitted"/>
                        </incipit>
                         </msItem>
                         <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.1.3">
                            <locus from="44v" to="46r" facs="045"/>
                            <title type="complete" ref="LIT5888AsmatPrayer"> Prayer to Christ for mercy</title>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                          ክርስቶስ፡ መሐረኒ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ተሣሃለኒ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ርድአኒ፡ ርድአኒ፡<gap reason="omitted"/>እስመ፡ አንተ፡ ውእቱ፡ ትመይጥ፡ ምክሮሙ፡ ለመለእክት፡ በክስብኤል፡<gap reason="omitted"/>
                        </incipit>
                         </msItem>
                         <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.1.4">
                            <locus from="46r" to="48v" facs="046"/>
                            <title type="complete" ref="LIT5888AsmatPrayer"> Prayer of salvation that descended to St. Thomas from heaven</title>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                          በስመ፡ አብ፡<gap reason="omitted"/>ጸሎተ፡ መድኃኒት፡ አስማተ፡ ኃያላን፡ ዘወረ፡ እምሰማያት።ዘወሀቦ፡ ለቶማስ፡ ረድዕ<gap reason="omitted"/>ኢያኤል፡ አፍናኤል፡ አስናኤል፡<gap reason="omitted"/>
                        </incipit>
                         </msItem>
                   </msItem>
                   <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.2"><locus target="#52r" facs="052"/><title>Sunday</title></msItem>
                   <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.3"><locus target="#62r" facs="062"/><title>Monday</title>
                   <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.3.1">
                     <locus from="62r" to="66v" facs="062"/>
                     <title type="complete" ref="LIT5888AsmatPrayer"> <foreign xml:lang="gez"/> prayer that God gave to Peter</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                       በስመ፡ አብ፡<gap reason="omitted"/>ጸሎቱ፡ ጴጥሮስ፡ ዝውእቱ፡ ዘየዓቢ፡ እምሐዋርያቲሁ፡ ዘኃረዮ፡ ክርስቶስ፡<gap reason="omitted"/>ወጸውዖሙ፡ ለኵሎሙ፡ ሐዋርያቲሁ፡<gap reason="omitted"/>ወይቤሎሙ፡ አንትሙ፡ አርዳእየ፡<gap reason="omitted"/>
                     </incipit>
                   </msItem>
                 </msItem>
                 <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.4"><locus from="67v" to="72r" facs="068"/><title>No day of the week assigned</title></msItem>
                   <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.4.1">
                     <locus from="67v" to="72r" facs="068"/>
                     <title type="incomplete" ref="LIT5888AsmatPrayer"> Prayer about which the angels asked the Lord</title>
                     <note>Incomplete at the beginning</note>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                       ወቤላሁ፡ ወዋቅሕት፡ አድማስ፡ ለእግዚእ፡ ኢትመጥነ፡ ለግሙራ፡ እመ፡ ኢይነክዩ፡ ሕዝብ፡ አንብአ፡ ከመ፡ ክረምት፡ ወካዕበ፡ ይቤላ፡ ለመዋቅሕት፡ አድማስ፡ ኢታውርደነ፡ ምስለ፡ ዲያብሎስ፡ ለእኩይ፡<gap reason="omitted"/>
                     </incipit>
                   </msItem>
                   <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.5"><locus target="#72r" facs="072"/><title>Thursday</title>
                   <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.5.1">
                     <locus from="72r" to="77r" facs="072"/>
                     <title type="complete" ref="LIT5888AsmatPrayer"> Prayer given to the Apostles and Mary</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                       በስመ፡ አብ፡<gap reason="omitted"/>አነ፡ ለሐዋርያት፡ ወሀበነ፡ ዘንተ፡ አስማተ፡ በደብረ፡ ዘይት፡ ወምስሌነ፡ እሙ፡ አመ፡ ዕለተ፡ ዕርገቱ፡<gap reason="omitted"/>
                       ወይቤለነ፡ ንሥዑ፡ ዘንተ፡ አስማተ፡ ይኩንኩሙ፡ ጽንአ፡ ኀበ፡ ተሐውሩ፡<gap reason="omitted"/>
                     </incipit>
                   </msItem>
                 </msItem>
                 <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.6"><locus target="#77r" facs="077"/><title>Friday</title>
                 <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.6.1">
                   <locus from="77r" to="82r" facs="077"/>
                   <title type="complete" ref="LIT5888AsmatPrayer"> The prayer, “May the names of Christ sanctify us.”</title>
                   <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                     በስመ፡ አብ፡<gap reason="omitted"/>ይቀድሰነ፡ አስማቲሁ፡ ለክርስቶስ፡ ሲድላዊ፡ ሊደጋዊ፡ ተድሮፋፈቃዲ፡<gap reason="omitted"/>
                   </incipit>
                 </msItem>
               </msItem>
               <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.7"><locus target="#82r" facs="082"/><title>Saturday</title>
               <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.7.1">
                 <locus from="82r" to="88r" facs="082"/>
                 <title type="complete" ref="LIT5888AsmatPrayer"> Prayer of the Apostles and Disciples for the forgiveness of sin</title>
                 <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                   በስመ፡ አብ፡<gap reason="omitted"/>ጸሎት፡ ሥርየት፡ እምነቶሙ፡ ለሐዋርያት፡ ወለኵሎሙ፡ ፸ወ፪አርድዕት፡ ከማሁ፡ ይቤሎሙ፡ ለአርዳኢሁ፡ አንቱሙ፡ ውእቱ፡ አዕርክትየ፡ ወይቤሎ፡ ጴጥሮስ፡ አንተ፡ ውእቱ፡ ጴጥሮስ፡<gap reason="omitted"/>
                 </incipit>
               </msItem>
             </msItem>
             <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.8"><locus target="#88r" facs="088"/><title>Sunday</title>
             <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.8.1">
               <locus from="88r" to="91v" facs="088"/>
               <title type="complete" ref="LIT5888AsmatPrayer"> Prayer that God gave to Ananiah, Azariah and Michael</title>
               <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                 በስመ፡ አብ፡<gap reason="omitted"/>ብርሃናኤል፡ ኦጕደ፡ ጽድቅ፡ አግላላኤል፡ ዘንተል
                 አስማተ፡ ዘወሀቦ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ለአናንያ፡ ወአዛርያ፡ ወሚሳኤል፡ እንዘ፡
                 ትይናገሮሙ፡ ለሚካኤል፡ ቀዊሞ፡ ማእከለ፡ እቶነ፡ እሳት፡<gap reason="omitted"/>
               </incipit>
             </msItem>
             </msItem>
             <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.9"><title>No day of the week assinged</title>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.9.1">
                        <locus from="91v" to="95v" facs="092"/>
                        <title type="complete" ref="LIT5888AsmatPrayer"> Prayer that Our Lord told to St. Andrew</title>
                        <incipit>
                      በስመ፡ አብ፡<gap reason="omitted"/>አስማት፡ ዘነግሮ፡ እግዚእነ፡ ለቅዱስ፡ እንድርያስ፡
                      ረድአ፡ ሐዋርያ፡ ወሰማዕት፡ ጸሎተ፡<gap reason="omitted"/>ወይቤሎ፡ ሑር፡ ሀገረ፡ በላዕተ፡
                      ሰብእ፡ ኀበ፡ ሀሎ፡ እኁከ፡ ማትያስ፡ ከመ፡ ታውጽኦ፡ እቤተ፡ ሞቅሕ፡<gap reason="omitted"/>
                    </incipit>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.9.2">
                        <locus from="95v" to="96r" facs="096"/>
                        <title type="complete" ref="LIT5888AsmatPrayer"> Prayer about the angel of death.</title>
                        <incipit>
                      በስመ፡ አብ፡<gap reason="omitted"/>ተማኅፀንኩ፡ ከመ፡ ኢይሙት፡ ዘእንበለ፡ ጊዜየ፡ ከመ፡
                      ሠራቂ፡ ሌሊት፡ ወከመ፡ ሠራቂ፡ መዓልት፡ በመንግሥት፡
                      አብ፡ ወወልድ፡<gap reason="omitted"/>ዘኢያድለቀልቅ፡ ሞርሞራ፡<gap reason="omitted"/>
                    </incipit>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.9.3">
                        <locus from="96v" to="100r" facs="097"/>
                        <title type="complete" ref="LIT5888AsmatPrayer"> Prayer that the angels told Enoch</title>
                        <incipit>
                      በስመ፡ አብ፡<gap reason="omitted"/>አስማት፡ ዘተናገርዎ፡ መላእክት፡ ለኄኖክ፡ ዘንተ፡
                      ወመሕርዎ፡ ወይቤልዎ፡ ሶበ፡ መጽአ፡ ድልቅልቅ፡ ወበረድ፡ ወጽዓእ፡
                      ወረኃብ፡ ለብሔር፡ ከመዝ፡ በል፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ጕንደ፡ መዓት፡ ወብዙኃ፡ ምኅረት፡<gap reason="omitted"/>
                    </incipit>
                     </msItem>
